_:Nd3c7057eb14e4bd1b87b2bbb16d0fdbe <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Use these contacts for all media enquiries, including enquiries outside office hours.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact contact\" id=\"contact_3306\">\n    <p class=\"govuk-body\">Matt Legg, Head of External Communications</p>\n\n\n    <div>\n        <p class=\"govuk-body govuk-!-margin-bottom-4\">\n          Email <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"mailto:external.relations@sellafieldsites.com\">external.relations@sellafieldsites.com</a>\n        </p>\n\n\n        <p class=\"govuk-body govuk-!-margin-bottom-4\">\n          Mobile 07748 777972\n        </p>\n    </div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"contact contact\" id=\"contact_7646\">\n    <p class=\"govuk-body\">Ben Chilton, Media contact</p>\n\n\n    <div>\n        <p class=\"govuk-body govuk-!-margin-bottom-4\">\n          Email <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"mailto:external.relations@sellafieldsites.com\">external.relations@sellafieldsites.com</a>\n        </p>\n\n\n        <p class=\"govuk-body govuk-!-margin-bottom-4\">\n          Mobile 07841153184\n        </p>\n    </div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n<p>Follow us on <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.twitter.com/sellafieldLtd\">Twitter</a>, <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SellafieldLtd\">Facebook</a>, <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/sellafieldsites\">YouTube</a>, <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/sellafield-ltd/\">LinkedIn</a> and <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/Sellafield\">Instagram</a></p>\n\n<p>If you are not a member of the media, please use <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/sellafield-ltd#org-contacts\">one of our other contacts</a>.</p>\n</div>" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
